{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CARD DRAW\u00a0</strong>is a relaxing roguelike deck builder where you construct equations with your cards to earn points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409750/extras/widget_gif_1.gif?t=1736167860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HOW TO PLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Draw cards from your deck to <strong>create equations</strong> and <strong>earn points</strong> for your <strong>final score</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use ability cards to discover <strong>strategies and synergies</strong> to earn even more points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spend points</strong> in the <strong>shop </strong>to <strong>expand your deck</strong> with\u00a0<strong>new cards and abilities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your score is your currency</strong>: points you spend in the shop\u00a0are deducted from your score, you should carefully determine when it's time to stop buying cards\u00a0and start accumulating points.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409750/extras/widget_gif_4.gif?t=1736167860\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEMO CONTENT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2 GAME MODES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RELAXING MODE</strong><br>Click to draw cards and automatically create equations to score points</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>STRATEGIC MODE</strong> <br>Draw and manually place cards to craft the perfect equations and score even more points</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 GAME DURATION VARIANTS</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SHORT, MEDIUM &amp; LONG</strong>\u00a0<br>Based on the game variant you choose, you'll have from 100 to 1000 draws to get the highest score possible with your cards</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>100+\u00a0</strong>card &amp; ability types</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards to score points for your score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use ability cards as passives to influence your runs</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARDS</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even more features </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Games summaries and graphs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Track player and game stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adjust settings for audio, screen, gameplay and other aspects of the game</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409750/extras/widget_gif_2.gif?t=1736167860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FULL GAME CONTENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to the content of this demo, the upcoming full game will include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>5 NEW GAME MODES</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SURVIVAL MODE</strong><br>Level up and survive for as many turns as possible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IDLE MODE</strong> <br>Watch your score grow while you do other things</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ADVENTURE MODE</strong> <br>Solve quests to earn new draws and play longer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DECKBUILDER MODE</strong> <br>Craft the perfect deck with the cards in your collection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CHALLENGE MODE</strong> <br>Solve challenges and math puzzles with your cards</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>1000+ </strong>new\u00a0card &amp; ability types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>STEAM ACHIEVEMENTS</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenges,<strong>\u00